ized by a cosmic vector with a non-zero\ncosmological mass scale. We also obtain the massless graviton and massive\nspinnon. We show a mechanism for quantum inflation caused by the quantum loop\ncontributions. The Einstein theory of general relativity is expected to be an\neffective low energy theory. Two types of gravity equation are resulted.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Oct 2015 21:21:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-04"}
