ies our previous argument that many of\nthe LABs in the SSA22 protocluster associated with multiple developed stellar\ncomponents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Oct 2015 08:35:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-09"}
