, the resemblance with our cosmic\nneighborhood extends to a few megaparsecs (< 5 Mpc/h). The simulations provide\na proper Large Scale environment for studies of the formation of nearby\nobjects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Oct 2015 14:44:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-19"}
